      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Real-world example"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Staging ECS task: AGENT_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini, ENABLE_DELETE_TOOL=false. Prod: gpt-4o, false. Canary prod task: new prompt via PROMPT_VERSION=v3 env pointing to S3 prompt bundle. Secrets from AWS Secrets Manager injected as OPENAI_API_KEY. App logs effective config at startup (redacted)."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Common mistakes"
          }
        ]
